title: PluralSight Marketing and Selling Your Own Products and Services
description:
PluralSight Marketing and Selling Your Own Products and Services Tutorial


Marketing and sales are foundational to the success of
your business, either the one you work in or the one you
run. This course walks you through concepts, ideas, models
and tools to better understand marketing and sales. We talk
about specific, actionable tactics that you can implement
to help you sell more, or to support your company in its
marketing and sales efforts. This course will also help you
understand business in general, and how some of the pieces
of business fit together
